race.comment: DRINK TINS (8) is a progressive type who recorded his 15th career win last time out (25.22) at Q Lakeside. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Can make it back-to-back wins. EXTREME TENSION (3) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won three of six starts. Hit the frame latest (25.38) when second at Q Lakeside in a OPEN. Looks one of the chances. AIDAN'S QUEEN (1) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (30.01) behind Fanciful at this track. Hard to beat again. GARRISON (4) is worth a look over a shorter journey this time.
